{"tid":2232914,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[買機送暖爐]測試版XSX好靜但係熱到仆街 直播主持俾張SSD卡辣親手","createTime":"2020-10-06T17:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T06:10:47.000Z","uid":39826,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7e0b084c7e8ba9d30b65a1dbd239c4e2545a1d44","tid":2232914,"uid":39826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T17:01:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.videogameschronicle.com/news/journalist-says-xbox-series-x-can-get-hot-like-a-fireplace/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.videogameschronicle.com%2Fnews%2Fjournalist-says-xbox-series-x-can-get-hot-like-a-fireplace%2F&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=11ae77f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.videogameschronicle.com/news/journalist-says-xbox-series-x-can-get-hot-like-a-fireplace/</a><br />\n<br />\nJeux Video&rsquo;s Ken Bogard&nbsp;echoed others&rsquo; praise for the quietness of the console&rsquo;s cooling system, but expressed surprise at how much heat the console emits as a result.<br />\n<br />\nHe said (translated by VGC): &ldquo;The Series X is hot, like really hot! It doesn&rsquo;t make any noise, but damn it&rsquo;s hot! The console is emitting heat like crazy. <span class=\"red\">It&rsquo;s almost like a fireplace shaft. You can heat up your flat with it.</span>&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nGiant Bomb co-host Jeff Bakkalar said his pre-release console was emitting a significant amount of heat even when in standby mode, and <span class=\"red\">even appeared to burn his hand on its storage expansion during a live stream.</span><br />\n<br />\n咁辣手即係應該表示XSX散熱能力非常強勁<br />\n<br />\n唔知另一邊廂Sony收收埋埋究竟想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能PS4PRO嘅飛機引擎聲升級到去A380級都未定<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab71d93e7d2d0af86a26dec0acb872e95abfbab","tid":2232914,"uid":161098,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T17:30:10.000Z","msg